  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT MAKING AN APPROPRIATION TO THE CITY OF HATTIESBURG, MISSISSIPPI, FOR THE PURPOSE OF DEFRAYING COSTS ASSOCIATED WITH IMPROVEMENTS IN ITS VETERANS DISTRICT AREA OF ITS DOWNTOWN, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO, VETERANS FACILITIES, ROADS, DRAINAGE, SIDEWALKS, STORMWATER DETENTION, LAND ACQUISITION, UTILITY RELOCATION AND LIGHTING FOR THE FISCAL YEAR 2027."
